=================================
Setting up Scala
=================================
1. Download Scala
wget http://downloads.lightbend.com/scala/2.12.1/scala-2.12.1.tgz

2. Unzip Scala
tar -xvzf scala-2.12.1.tgz


=================================
Running LinearInterpolation
=================================
0. Unzip A1.tgz
tar -xvzf A1.tgz

1. Launch the script
scala -J-Xmx2g  LinearInterpolation.scala

2. Enter the input parameters (see HyperParameters.xlsx for Hyper-parameters)
brown,brown,0.1,0.5,0.4

3. Output shows up as follows
brown,brown,0.1,0.5,0.4,263.19866712723984


=================================
Running Back-off
=================================
0. Unzip A1.tgz
tar -xvzf A1.tgz

1. Launch the script
scala -J-Xmx2g  Backoff.scala

2. Enter the input parameters (see HyperParameters.xlsx for Hyper-parameters)
brown,brown,0.8

3. Output shows up as follows
brown,brown,0.8,246.85226656254218